Relative clauses and WH-questions
what did a man eat
where does mary walk
what did a man think
when does john walk in the garden
whom did john see in the garden
where did he sleep
why did john go to houston
what did mary give to john
the elephant eats the man that eats the apple that the flies eat
a man saw an elephant who ate a banana that mary gave
an elephant sleeps in the garden where the flies book a flight
john walks in the garden where mary sees the flies that fly
the flies eat an elephant that eats the apple that mary gave to a man who saw john in houston
john eats mary who books a flight to the garden where an apple eats an elephant
mary saw an apple that john ate in the garden when he saw an elephant